{"type": "article", "id": 25211, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。", "date": "2016-04-10T07:00:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 214, "name": "NASA"}, {"id": 10012, "name": "美国偶像"}, {"id": 1510, "name": "猫"}], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 189, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071605324xUp8HDbk3rF69AE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h2>\n<blockquote><b>涂红的手掌</b></blockquote>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160527S0teZTQcdRmCxiFK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">PATRICK BAZ/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">黎巴嫩贝鲁特（Beirut），抗议者在手掌中涂上红色颜料前往正义宫（Justice Palace）前示威，抗议卖淫、性奴役以及针对女性的暴力。<br></p>\n<blockquote><b>视线</b></blockquote>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060716052709sLZkcwE8XuS3AP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">GREG BAKER/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">中国仪仗队士兵为瑞士联邦主席施奈德-阿曼（Johann Schneider-Ammann）访华做准备。<br></p>\n<blockquote><b>古城中的工程兵</b></blockquote>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160528ON0tlTkyudWf3KjY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">MAX DELANY/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">俄罗斯的工程兵在叙利亚的帕尔米亚古城展开行动。</p>\n<blockquote><b>国际空间站</b></blockquote>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160528qTDBmF19Qn6iHlr4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">在 NASA 发布的这张照片中，国际空间站正飞越马达加斯加上方。</p>\n<blockquote><b>美国偶像落幕</b></blockquote>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160529u7FCjDvebGBTaU4R.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">主持人詹妮弗·洛佩兹在美国偶像的告别集上落泪。</p>\n<h2>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h2>\n<blockquote><b>汉江边</b></blockquote>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160529UTL0IqpnH2CxrWhu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">杨东/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">湖北省襄阳市，汉江上空出现平流雾美景。 <br></p>\n<blockquote><b>飞絮如雪</b></blockquote>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160530lUSauIYKO1Z5QAwF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">胡斐/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">天津，纷纷扬扬的杨絮柳絮如同大雪飞洒。<br></p>\n<blockquote><b>俄罗斯馆喵</b></blockquote>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160530YQiqLCvpjm3gedor.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Vyacheslav Prokofyev/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">今年愚人节，谢尔普霍夫历史艺术博物馆（Serpukhov's Museum of History and Art）的员工发布<a href=\"http://serpuhov-museum.ru/novosti/529-muzejnyj-kot-po-imeni-maraj.html\">一则消息</a>说接受了一只猫咪的求职信。迫于公众的压力，这只名字叫“玛拉伊”（Marai）的小猫现在真的被博物馆聘用了。玛拉伊在博物馆的主要职责是迎接参观者，工资将以鱼和肉饼的形式发放。<br></p>\n<blockquote><b>兔子耳朵</b></blockquote>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160531W2o5twJfI0bAQaRp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">FRISO GENTSCH/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">一只野兔藏在德国 Hille 的一处草地中。</p>\n<blockquote><b>雪地极光</b></blockquote>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607160531jlO3Qz16bKWXERmv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Anadolu Agency/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">俄罗斯涅涅茨自治区（Yamalo-Nenets）的 Salekhard 镇附近出现的北极光。<br></p>\n\n\n"}